Description: mode for interacting with confluence wiki
 Confluence is a commercial Wiki engine and this package offer remote
 editing of its pages. Basic commands:
 .
    M-x confluence-get-page        Edit page at confluence Wiki server
    C-x C-s                        Push page back
    confluence-ediff-current-page  View chnages
